Dejavu Sans Mono for Powerline Book

* Install asdf
Install: git clone https://github.com/asdf-vm/asdf.git ~/.asdf --branch v0.7.8
Add to ~/.bashrc 

# Generic asdf Version Manager for Deno & Node
. $HOME/.asdf/asdf.sh
. $HOME/.asdf/completions/asdf.bash

Reload bashrc
source ~/.bashrc

Add Deno plugin
asdf plugin-add deno https://github.com/asdf-community/asdf-deno.git

Install Deno
asdf install deno latest

Activate Deno
asdf global deno 1.0.2 


